Class LoadAndSaveScratch3

java.lang.Object
com.marginallyclever.artPipeline.ImageManipulator
com.marginallyclever.artPipeline.loadAndSave.LoadAndSaveScratch3
All Implemented Interfaces:
LoadAndSaveFileType
public class LoadAndSaveScratch3
extends ImageManipulator
implements LoadAndSaveFileType
LoadAndSaveSB3 loads limited set of Scratch commands into memory. We ignore monitors, which are visual displays of variables, booleans, and lists. They don't contain any real information we need.
Author:
Dan Royer
